  <section>
    <h2>Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to make AI authorization dependable, reviewable, and operationally practical.
      BeaconGuard reduces ambiguity by separating policy control, enforcement, and evidence generation
      into a clear runtime boundary.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What We Are</h2>
    <p>
      BeaconGuard is an infrastructure product for enterprise teams building AI into
      mission-critical processes.
    </p>
    <p>
      We focus on deterministic policy enforcement and evidence-ready operations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      Enterprise teams need governance that scales with systems, not with exception handling.
      We built BeaconGuard for teams that want clear boundaries, replayable outcomes,
      and practical proof for governance and assurance conversations.
    </p>
  </section>

